name: OutRun 2006: Coast 2 Coast
description:
Give in to the power

Feel the power as you blip the throttle of your favorite Ferrari and blast across America from coast to glorious coast.

13 beautiful machines Take your emotion's for a ride in 13 different Ferrari car's.

30 exhilarating tracks 15 new US themed tracks and 15 original OutRun 2 arcade level's.

Wireless play Share your dream with 6 other player's.

OutRun miles Stack up OutRun miles to unlock new tracks, cars and much, much more.
